    "reviews": {
      "type": "lp-reviews-summary",
      "blocks": {
        "r1": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Carole j.", "rating": 5, "title": "Ridiculous but Amazing", "content": "<p>The shirt is adorable. I used a picture of our cat and it came out really clear. I was worried because the photo I uploaded wasn't the best quality, but Hapyco still made it look great. My husband said it's \"ridiculous but amazing\" and that's exactly what I wanted.</p>", "date": "May 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r2": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "ron d.", "rating": 5, "title": "The Perfect Gift for My Husband", "content": "<p>The shirt came out way better than I expected. I ordered it with pictures of our two dogs for my husband and he literally just stood there smiling when he opened it. The colors were bright, the dogs looked so clear, and the whole thing felt really personal. He wore it the same night to dinner and everyone kept asking where I got it from.</p>", "date": "May 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r3": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Tommy G.", "rating": 5, "title": "My Dad Showed Everyone", "content": "<p>I got this for my dad for Father's Day and he absolutely loved it. He doesn't usually get emotional over gifts but when he saw our old dog on the shirt he got quiet for a second and said \"this is actually really cool.\" That alone made it worth it. Thank you Hapyco.</p>", "date": "April 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r4": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Samuel p.", "rating": 5, "title": "Everyone Loved It at the BBQ", "content": "<p>This shirt was a huge hit for my boyfriend's birthday. I put our cat on it as a joke at first but when it arrived it looked so good that it didn't even feel like a joke anymore. He wore it to his birthday BBQ and people were stopping him all day to look at it. The quality was nicer than I expected too.</p>", "date": "April 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r5": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Alex N.", "rating": 4, "title": "Almost Perfect and So Meaningful", "content": "<p>I ordered one for my husband with our dog Max on it and it came out almost perfect. The print is beautiful and the picture looks exactly like him. My husband laughed first, then he actually got emotional because Max passed last year. The shirt fit him well, but the sleeves were maybe a tiny bit bigger than expected.</p>", "date": "April 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r6": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "John M.", "rating": 5, "title": "So Cute and Bright", "content": "<p>Honestly I wasn't sure how the photo would look on a Hawaiian shirt, but it came out so cute. The colors are bright, the fabric is light, and my dog's face is everywhere in the funniest way. My husband has already worn it twice.</p>", "date": "March 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r7": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Walt f.", "rating": 5, "title": "Strangers Kept Complimenting Him", "content": "<p>Bought this for my fiancé and he loved it. We went out for drinks and strangers kept complimenting the shirt. He was proud telling everyone it was our dog on it. Such a cool idea and really good quality.</p>", "date": "March 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } },
        "r8": { "type": "review", "settings": { "author": "Jeff C.", "rating": 5, "title": "Best Gift of the Party", "content": "<p>I surprised my brother with this shirt for his 40th birthday with his bulldog printed all over it. He opened it in front of everyone and the whole room started laughing and cheering. Then he put it on right away and didn't take it off the whole night. The shirt was definitely the best gift of the party.</p>", "date": "February 2026", "verified": true, "verified_label": "verified buyer" } }
      },
